<p><strong>AND</strong> <strong>Make sure to pick up your copy of The Star this Saturday November 14th!</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;An unaccompanied refugee minor, who recently stayed at Matthew House, will be featured in a piece by journalist&nbsp;Scott Simmie.</p></div>
